    "Parallel processing with Rayon 36 is employed to further speed up this process.",
    "Once completed, Benjamini-Hochberg adjusted p-values are computed.",
    "Next, the results are sorted by p-value, temporarily cached, and returned.",
    "The gene sets in Rummagene are stored in a Postgres database 37.",
    "A function in the Postgres database is responsible for mapping the gene symbols to UUIDs before passing them to the Rust API to obtain results."
